node.text: Hello Faves Mummy

My shot at motherhood has been filled with hits and misses. But that’s how life is! 🤷🏻‍♀️ Happy Mother’s Day to all mums, thanks for always trying to make life better for your kids 👍🏻.
.
To show my appreciation for my own mothers, I ordered wine to be delivered to them. Practical gift! 🤣 But my own kids didn’t get me anything 🙄. Did your kids prepare any surprises for you?.
.
.
.

Love practical gifts 👍 Happy Mother's Day to u too!
